":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:25:56.000Z","msg":"Dept of Joke"},{"pid":"098533ea0f78bccb0abc66bc235d3c18cfd3cf28","tid":2195102,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>作為被告人，受司法程序糾纏多時，耗費大量精力尋找片段自證清白，即使獲法庭判罪名不成立，過程中所受的困擾，難以彌補。</blockquote><br />\n鳩告點可以無後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼要賠返錢俾受害人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76f893f468554c034375b206e3fae1216528dd3d","tid":2195102,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b08f81cc782bd9583b6e4486360d04ef0fa97c","tid":2195102,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"法庭的確係冇權作出檢控"},{"pid":"596f9a455d849b1853d72b6bbe63404b96286ee4","tid":2195102,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"76f893f468554c034375b206e3fae1216528dd3d","tid":2195102,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1b08f81cc782bd9583b6e4486360d04ef0fa97c","tid":2195102,"uid":153811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T03:41:17.000Z","msg":"法庭的確係冇權作出檢控"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a231c9bef1e0d5ea9962c657e72d41307a2b35a","tid":2195102,"uid":365024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"596f9a455d849b1853d72b6bbe63404b96286ee4","tid":21